<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>My Own Cluster</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.3/css/bulma.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 15rem">
    <h1 class="title has-text-centered">
      My Own Cluster
    </h1>
    <div>
      <a
        class="button is-light is-large"
        style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 15rem; margin: 1rem auto;"
        href="//nomad.${domain}/">
        <img
          src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1620155098-brandhcnomadprimaryattributedcolor.svg"
          style="display: block; height: 3rem"
          alt="Nomad" />
      </a>
      <a
        class="button is-light is-large"
        style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 15rem; margin: 1rem auto;"
        href="//vault.${domain}/ui/vault/auth?with=userpass">
        <img
          src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1620159869-brandvaultprimaryattributedcolor.svg"
          style="display: block; height: 3rem"
          alt="Vault" />
      </a>
      <hr />
      <a
        class="button is-light is-large"
        style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 15rem; margin: 1rem auto; text-align: center;"
        href="//traefik.${domain}/">
        <img
          src="//traefik.${domain}/dashboard/assets/logo-C9XRQwqK.svg"
          style="display: block; height: 3rem"
          alt="Traefik" />
      </a>
      <a
        class="button is-light is-large"
        style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 15rem; margin: 1rem auto;"
        href="//consul.${domain}/">
        <img
          src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/2885/1620155090-brandhcconsulprimaryattributedcolor.svg"
          style="display: block; height: 3rem"
          alt="Consul" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="content has-text-centered">
    <p>In order to access these dashboards, you need to be connected to the WireGuard VPN, have configured the system DNS, and added <a href="ca.crt" download>the Vault certificate authority</a> to your browser's trusted store.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
